title: Witness: police fire rubber balls in Barcelona
description:
(1 Oct 2017) People in Barcelona showed injuries they say were sustained as a result of actions taken by police.
A man showed injuries to his leg and said he was fired on by police using rubber balls. 
Another man showed injuries to his back saying that "we have to protest in a non violent way but but how will we end up? This way."
Several people held up ball-like projectiles they said had been used in police actions.
